---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Construction | Bravura Builders"
  description="Full-service general contracting: luxury remodels, commercial renovations, and ground-up construction, priced with fixed line-item proposals. Free estimates."
>
  <section class="page-hero dark on-dark">
    <div class="wrap">
      <span class="eyebrow">Construction &middot; Free estimates</span>
      <h1>The number we quote is the number we build.</h1>
      <p class="lede">
        Every Bravura project runs on a line-item proposal, a deposit and milestone payment schedule
        you approve up front, and a schedule that gets managed, not hoped for.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section style="padding-top:0">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="svc4 stagger">
        <div class="svc-card rv">
          <span class="k">01 &middot; Residential</span><h3>Luxury remodels</h3><p>
            Kitchens, baths, and whole-home renovations finished to a standard you can inspect room
            by room.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="svc-card rv">
          <span class="k">02 &middot; Commercial</span><h3>Commercial renovations</h3><p>
            Offices, washrooms, and tenant build-outs. Insured, professional, and delivered on a
            real schedule.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="svc-card rv">
          <span class="k">03 &middot; Ground-up</span><h3>Ground-up construction</h3><p>
            From foundation to finish, managed by a team that has run large-scale builds in the most
            demanding market in the country.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="svc-card rv">
          <span class="k">04 &middot; Pre-construction</span><h3>
            Pre-construction &amp; estimating
          </h3><p>
            Feasibility, budgets, and line-item estimates that let you make the go or no-go call
            with real numbers.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="banner rv">
        <img
          src="/img/projects/DSC07598.jpg"
          alt="Renovated living room with restored original mantel and new white-oak floors"
          loading="lazy"
        /><div class="cap"><b>Parlor floor renovation</b><span>As built</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section style="padding-top:24px">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="sec-head rv">
        <div>
          <span class="eyebrow">How a project runs</span>
          <h2>Four steps. No surprises.</h2>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="steps stagger">
        <div class="step rv">
          <h3>Walkthrough</h3><p>
            We meet on site, measure, and listen. You get straight answers about scope and cost.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="step rv">
          <h3>Line-item proposal</h3><p>
            A written scope with per-item pricing. The estimate is free, and it&rsquo;s the number
            we stand behind.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="step rv">
          <h3>Deposit &amp; schedule</h3><p>
            A deposit plus milestone payments tied to real progress, agreed before work starts.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="step rv">
          <h3>Build &amp; handover</h3><p>
            A managed crew, progress updates, and a punch list closed before we call it done.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="cta-band" style="padding-top:0">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="cta-box rv">
        <div>
          <h2>Get your free estimate.</h2>
          <p>Send the basics and we&rsquo;ll call you back within one business day.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="actions">
          <a class="btn blue" href="/contact">Get a free estimate <span class="arr">&rarr;</span></a
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
